N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 23.4 - Corrected filings

State Regulations

If the reporting entity files a corrected call report with
the appropriate Federal regulatory authority, it will immediately notify the
superintendent in writing of such corrected filing. Notes
